<%- include('header.ejs'); %>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/styles.css" />

<section id="title">
  <div class="row">
    <div
      class="col-lg-6 greeting-text-div"
      
    >
      <h1 id="aayudh-text">
        We are "Team AAYUDH 2.0" representing Government College of
        Engineering and Research, Avasari Khurd in SAE TIFAN...
      </h1>
    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-6 ">
      <div
        id="carouselExampleControls"
        class="carousel slide"
        data-ride="carousel"
      >
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img
              class="carousel-img1"
              src="Images/carousel-1-img/shaurya-img.jpg"
              alt="First slide"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img
              class="carousel-img1"
              src="Images/carousel-1-img/2020.jpeg"
              alt="Second slide"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <a
          class="carousel-control-prev"
          href="#carouselExampleControls"
          role="button"
          data-slide="prev"
        >
          <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a
          class="carousel-control-next"
          href="#carouselExampleControls"
          role="button"
          data-slide="next"
        >
          <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="about">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="card-column col-lg-4 col-md-6">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h3>Who We Are</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p align="justify">
            We are team Aayudh 2.0 from the Government College of 
            Engineering and Research Avasari Khurd, Pune. We participate 
            in the event called SAE TIFAN. We are a team of undergraduate 
            engineering students from different streams. We are a part of SAE TIFAN 
            since 2017. We successfully manufactured “Self-Propelled Onion 
            Harvester” in the events of 2021 and 2022. Currently we are 
            designing a “Automatic Multi-Vegetable Transplanter”. 
            Making our technology society oriented is our key driving force.  
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card-column col-lg-4 col-md-6">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h3>What We Do</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="card-body">
          <p align="justify">
            We participate in the event called SAE TIFAN. 
            We Conceive, Design and Manufacture farm machinery 
            as per the guidelines given by the organizing committee. 
            We are a part of SAE TIFAN since 2017. We successfully 
            manufactured “Self-Propelled Harvester” in the events of 
            2021 and 2022. Currently, we are designing an “Automatic 
            Multi-Vegetable Transplanter”. Every machine is designed by always 
            considering the farmers' requirements and safety.   
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-column col-lg-4">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h3>Our Bussiness Impact</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p align="justify">
            We keep visiting the industries in Pune for their guidance and help 
            during our product fabrication process. Our work not only adds value 
            to the research in agriculture but also creates awareness among the 
            field people. By this, people will start thinking about mechanization 
            and its benefits in the future for sure. Since, we belong to a remote 
            area it’s a very good opportunity for businesses to reach our market through us. 
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div
    id="carouselExampleIndicators"
    class="carousel slide"
    data-ride="carousel"
  >
    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
      <li
        data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators"
        data-slide-to="0"
        class="active"
      ></li>
      <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
      <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
    </ol>
    <div class="carousel-img carousel-inner">
      <div class="carousel-item active">
        <img
          class="d-block w-100"
          src="Images/shaurya-img.jpg"
          alt="First slide"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-img carousel-item">
        <img
          class="d-block w-100"
          src="Images/team_photo.jpg"
          alt="Second slide"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    <a
      class="carousel-control-prev"
      href="#carouselExampleIndicators"
      role="button"
      data-slide="prev"
    >
      <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a
      class="carousel-control-next"
      href="#carouselExampleIndicators"
      role="button"
      data-slide="next"
    >
      <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sponsors">
  <h3>Our Sponsors</h3>
  <div class="row">
    <% sponsors.forEach(function(sponsor){ %>
    <div class="col-4 col-lg-2 col-md-4 col-sm-4" style="margin: auto">
      <img
        class="sponsors-logo"
        src="<%=sponsor.src%>"
        alt="<%=sponsor.logo%>"
      />
    </div>
    <% }) %>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('footer.ejs'); %>
